OL,3,CMountain rescue team wants to become
OL,4,CUK's first to pilot drones remotely
OL,6,FThe Wasdale Mountain Rescue team wants
OL,7,Fto become the first in the UK to be
OL,8,Fable to remotely use drones to provide
OL,9,Fassistance to those in need.
OL,11,FThe team has seen drones become an
OL,12,Fincreasingly important tool in its
OL,13,Farsenal, but currently regulations
OL,14,Frequire that a drone operator must
OL,15,Fhave the drone in their sight at all
OL,16,Ftimes.
OL,18,FWasdale Mountain Rescue now wants
OL,19,Fapproval to be able to fly drones
OL,20,Fbeyond the visual line of sight.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
