PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774372288
OL,3,CMountain rescue team wants to become
OL,4,CUK's first to pilot drones remotely
OL,6,FRichard Warren OBE from the team said:
OL,7,F"We could, with authorisation, fly a
OL,8,Fdefibrillator to the top of Scafell
OL,9,FPike from the road head, lower it, and
OL,10,Fit's a very simple piece of equipment
OL,11,Fto use.
OL,13,F"Or it could be a tent if (the
OL,14,Fcasualty) is cold, a bottle of water,
OL,15,For food.
OL,17,F"We are planning to have that in place
OL,18,Ffor Wasdale before the autumn."
OL,26,@uD@[pmvD@Ipn
