FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774372288
OL,3,CMountain rescue team wants to become
OL,4,CUK's first to pilot drones remotely
OL,6,FIt currently takes volunteers around
OL,7,Fan hour to reach the summit of Scafell
OL,8,FPike, and the rescue team says remote
OL,9,Fdrone operation could get medical aid
OL,10,Fwhere it is needed in a fraction of
OL,11,Fthe time.
OL,13,FThe team has long-term plans to have
OL,14,Fdrones permanently stationed around
OL,15,Fthe Fells, which could be instantly
OL,16,Fpiloted by a volunteer from a laptop
OL,17,Fto pinpoint the casualty while rescue
OL,18,Fvolunteers kit up.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
