FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774372288
OL,3,CMountain rescue team wants to become
OL,4,CUK's first to pilot drones remotely
OL,6,FThis technology is already being used
OL,7,Fby Wasdale Mountain Rescue to find
OL,8,Fpeople, with a pilot launching and
OL,9,Fmonitoring the drone while within
OL,10,Feyesight.
OL,12,FThe drone surveys an area and looks
OL,13,Ffor colours which do not match the
OL,14,Fsurrounding area.
OL,16,FRemote drone operation will require
OL,17,Fapproval from the Civil Aviation
OL,18,FAuthority before the mountain rescue
OL,19,Fteam can achieve their goal before
OL,20,Fautumn.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
